Marlan is a simple tool for editing and presenting files in the browser, by Eric Danielson (http://danielsoneg.com) and Harlan Lewis (http://harlanlewis.com).

It's built in Python with Tornado (http://tornadoweb.org), Sass (http://sass-lang.com), jQuery (http://jquery.com), and the Dropbox API (http://dropbox.com/developers).